##This is their diary of the plague, but also a precious memory of the Times

Micro-signal Jianjiaobuluo

Function description, pepper tribe, amplify your voice! Chinese Women Workers Exclusive Information Platform, you are welcome to pay attention!

ABSTRACT: "Why should I be busier than at work when I have no job? "

How would you spend your time away from home?
For some women, the answer is that they are just as busy at home as they are at home.
The greenbrier social work service center and the pepper tribe have launched a day of the worker in the epidemic | 2020 International Women's Day photo and essay collection, and received many wonderful contributions from their sisters. They use photos and text to record their ordinary and rich day, but also to record the neglected, condensed in the daily necessities, Three Meals a Day behind the hard work.

Rainbows
Take care of a large family's daily routine.

It was a fine day, and I washed a large family of clothes.

While the kids are at home, make them something nice to eat every day.

I packed enough steamed buns with my kids and my husband to last a while.

Go to the fields and see how the medicated wheat is doing.

The Sun was so warm that I took my mother's quilt out to dry.

Two. Two
Enjoy life. Enjoy the company.

Every day is the sun to wake up their own, one-meter Balcony Sunshine breakfast, playing light music, soothing every moment.

I don't want to take too long for lunch. Keep it simple. I'm GONNA need some time to draw.

Painted Lotus, painted Mei Lan Zhu Ju, today also painted the first round fan, but also want to blow pottery Xun, also want to practice calligraphy. Alas, time flies.


I have to get ready early tomorrow morning. Everyone's a master chef, including me.

Daughter came back from work, the night of hot pot walk.

I'm ready to go to the movies. I've never had the chance to see so many big movies. After watching them, I talked with my daughter about their feelings. It is a rare opportunity to discuss current affairs and exchange ideas with young people. It is very enjoyable and wonderful.
In fact, from the beginning because of the epidemic news every day crying, and then every day full of schedule, quiet and enjoy life, is just a matter of mentality.
Spring comes anyway, doesn't it.

Ming-ho's mom
Suspended, but the kids can't be suspended.

Get up in the morning and cook breakfast for Ming Hao.

Ming Hao to arrange a study plan, suspended without suspension, at home can study independently.

Originally I was a working mother, the sudden outbreak of the disease disrupted my life, and now I have become an unemployed mother. But I do not know why, I obviously do not have a job, why than to work also busy? It all started with my son.
I did have a very busy day, get up early to make breakfast for my son to eat, after breakfast to give him homework, he did homework, I do sanitation, laundry, finished the housework, but also to give my son lessons. This is my son and I do "learning Corner" , let him learn every day to write out the knowledge, their paste up.

This moment is a parent-child activity time, with him to exercise together, he jumped I count, I jump he count. Home Exercise, good health, good food, but also to grow tall. If you exercise your body well, your resistance will naturally increase.

Prepare Dinner, and wait for the father to come home for dinner.

Parent-child reading, reading picture books with children, can enhance the mother-child relationship, a good story a day, accompany children happy growth.
Unconsciously, a day on this way, ordinary and simple happiness. My Day is pretty much all about the kids.

Hey, jace
A day as a stay-at-home mom.

A really busy day begins the moment darling wakes up. Before Darling wakes up, get out of bed, wash up, make breakfast, and get the kids'clothes ready. The worst part was that before I finished my breakfast, both of them woke up at the same time and had to run back and forth all morning.

Lunch is generally to eat around 1:00 pm, after feeding my brother, the dishes have been cold, I can only eat in a hurry, fill the stomach on the line. Then to coax brother (Dabao) NAP, sister (Xiaobao) do touch, help brain development, practice head, and then coax sister to sleep.

When he woke up in the afternoon, it was time to prepare tea for his chickens and ducks. Xiao Bao was still sleeping, and he took Taih≈ç to the vegetable patch at the gate to pick up some vegetables and chop them up for the chickens.

Dinner is served at 4:30: Fried snails. Washing the snails is a chore. You have to brush them off one by one.

After dinner, at about eight o'clock, he began to bathe the two little ones and tell them bedtime stories. It's usually around 10:30 before both babies fall asleep.

Two treasures have time to sleep to shower, put a family off the clothes washed, and then began to clean up the house, do health, it is nearly twelve o'clock.
Everything was done, and then... Xiao Bao woke up again. It was time to get the milk powder

Snow Plum
The rape flowers are in full bloom in the field.

February 2 Dragon head up, mother-in-law said to eat dumplings in the morning.

It was half the morning after breakfast. Long time no go out, the storage of vegetables have already finished, fortunately there is a vegetable field, go to the ground pull some vegetables ready lunch.

After lunch, and her mother-in-law to gather firewood in the field, dried can be pulled back to burn pot.

The Rape Flowers in the field are very beautiful.

I watch my nieces and nephews take online lessons at night, while my husband gives them extra lessons. Old People don't know how to watch online classes without young people in their homes. There is no Internet at home, no traffic, children learn online class is like watching TV, you will hear: "This episode is over. "

How would you spend your time away from home?

For some women, the answer is that they are just as busy at home as they are at home.
